4.62	Homie_the_Clown	Homie the Clown	"Homie the Clown" is the 15th episode of The Simpsons' sixth season, and aired on February 12, 1995. When Krusty the Clown opens a clown college to deal with his debt, Homer Simpson enrolls and ends up impersonating Krusty at public events. Mistaking him for the real clown, the Springfield Mafia kidnaps Homer, demanding their money. Joe Mantegna returned as Fat Tony, while Dick Cavett and Johnny Unitas guest starred as themselves.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e5/Homie_the_Clown.png/235px-Homie_the_Clown.png
